                    <dcc:content lang="en">Calibration function (Steinhart-Hart): 1/T[K] = a + b*ln(R) + c*ln(R)^3. Coefficients: a=5.983542e-04 (u=2.91e-01), b=2.400726e-04 (u=3.94e-02), c=-1.648966e-09 (u=1.01e-04).</dcc:content>
